{"type":"message","id":"aa1baaf1","parentId":"44113432","timestamp":"2026-03-27T04:21:57.619Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"mihomo-party 在运行，sidecar 进程监听 Unix socket。可能还监听了 HTTP 代理端口。需要检查配置。看看环境变量：`env | grep -i proxy`。另外检查 Docker 代理配置：`systemctl show docker --property=Environment` 或者 `cat ~/.docker/config.json`。\n\n但根据规则，代理栈是受保护的，不能修改。不过可以检查当前代理设置是否影响了 Docker。错误信息显示代理连接被拒绝，可能是代理没有监听 5872 端口，或者 Docker 配置了错误的代理。\n\n先检查端口监听：`ss -tlnp | grep :5872`。如果没监听，可能是代理配置的端口不同。检查 mihomo 的配置目录：`/home/asus/.config/mihomo-party/` 看看 config.yaml。\n\n但注意，我不能修改这些配置，只能读取查看。让我先检查端口。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_9iWGaIrzP52kM8cwXsiLmKRC","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ss -tlnp | grep :5872"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":1138,"output":436,"cacheRead":15168,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":16742,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774585307145,"responseId":"96fca5f0-9d33-45a4-9e79-ecbd538d586b"}}
