{"type":"message","id":"0569f3b2","parentId":"646f1115","timestamp":"2026-03-27T04:22:51.911Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"可能是动态端口。检查 sidecar 进程实际监听的端口：`ss -tlnp | grep mihomo`。或者查看进程参数。但问题在于 Docker 连接 5872 端口被拒绝。这个端口可能是 Docker 配置的代理。检查 Docker 的代理配置：`systemctl show docker --property=Environment 2>/dev/null`。如果没有 systemctl，检查 `/etc/default/docker` 或 `/etc/docker/daemon.json`。\n\n先检查 Docker 服务环境：","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_vTVxhxGRnBwCgOoyZUgDALS8","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"systemctl show docker --property=Environment 2>/dev/null || echo \"Cannot read systemctl\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":200,"output":279,"cacheRead":18176,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18655,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774585365345,"responseId":"c5572291-ac71-4445-a1e0-de356be4e836"}}
