{"type":"message","id":"af39b6f8","parentId":"2a5243f9","timestamp":"2026-03-27T04:53:40.776Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"网关正在运行。现在尝试发送消息给offense agent。\n\n使用`sessions_send`，设置`agentId: \"offense\"`，`message: \"扫描周围 CMCC 热点。\"`。但需要确保这个任务描述清晰。实际上，我们需要发送一个更详细的任务说明。\n\n但首先，我们只发送一个简单的消息来测试offense agent是否能响应。如果它回复了，那么我们就可以继续发送更详细的任务。\n\n另外，考虑到之前创建的子代理失败是因为沙箱限制，也许offense agent配置了不同的沙箱策略？需要检查offense agent的配置。可能位于`~/.openclaw/agents/offense/agent/`目录下。但那里只有auth和models文件。配置可能在workspace目录中：`~/.openclaw/workspaces/offense/`。现在查看一下。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_yPcP3O1jGQ7un1poMqBdgAYx","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"ls -la /home/asus/.openclaw/workspaces/offense/"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":691,"output":416,"cacheRead":61248,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":62355,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774587211549,"responseId":"cd89f0ce-905a-4823-a8ae-5895eb1c8106"}}
