{"type":"message","id":"19939567","parentId":"99af55c5","timestamp":"2026-03-27T05:01:15.700Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户对当前的架构是否落实了他想要的理想架构感到困惑。我需要回顾一下之前的对话。\n\n用户之前指出有三类代理：指挥官、攻击者、防御者。他问我为什么创建这么多子代理去执行攻击任务，而不是直接告诉已有的agent执行任务。我解释了因为攻击者代理没有活跃会话，所以创建了子代理作为临时执行单元。用户选择了A方案：启动攻击者代理并直接通信。我尝试用OpenClaw CLI启动攻击者代理，但命令挂起了，我杀死了它。然后用户说\"B\"，我理解为选择方案B（创建持久攻击者会话）。我创建了一个子代理标签为\"offense-main\"，但它完成了（单次任务模式）。现在用户说他不明白架构是否落实到了他想要的理想架构。\n\n用户想要的理想架构是：指挥官（我）分析、委托；攻击者（offense）执行攻击任务；防御者（defense）执行防御任务。指挥官不应该亲自执行操作，而应该将任务委托给相应的代理。\n\n目前的实际情况是：\n- 指挥官（我）在运行。\n- 攻击者代理（offense）已配置但无活跃会话。我尝试通过CLI启动失败。\n- 防御者代理（defense）类似。\n- 我创建了许多子代理来执行攻击任务，但这些子代理是在我的会话下创建的，违背了\"指挥官只委托不执行\"的原则。\n\n用户可能想要的是：攻击者和防御者作为独立的、持久的代理运行，我可以直接通过sessions_send向它们发送任务。而不是每次创建子代理。\n\n我需要澄清当前状态：我们还没有实现理想的架构。攻击者代理没有作为独立持久会话运行。我创建的子代理是临时的，且是在我的会话下创建的。\n\n那么，我应该解释现状，并提出明确的步骤来实现理想架构。可能的方案：\n1. 尝试通过OpenClaw系统启动独立的offense代理实例（可能通过openclaw node或gateway命令）。\n2. 或者创建一个长期运行的子代理（offense-persistent），但这次要确保它真正持续运行并可以接收消息。\n3. 或者配置路由绑定，使offense代理在特定条件下自动启动。\n\n我需要检查OpenClaw文档或尝试其他命令来启动独立代理。先看看是否有openclaw node命令。之前看到有openclaw node *命令。也许可以用openclaw node start或类似命令。\n\n但首先，我需要回应用户的困惑，说明现状与理想架构的差距，然后提出具体解决方案。我将建议尝试启动独立的offense代理实例，或者创建长期子代理。用户之前说\"B\"，可能倾向于持久会话方案。\n\n我需要用清晰的语言解释，然后给出选择。现在开始行动。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_n41TwQFdhySwwn3WrzKdsweQ","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw node --help"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":1327,"output":1170,"cacheRead":71296,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73793,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774587652770,"responseId":"093e3639-8a81-45db-ac8c-cb40b87b3d5b"}}
{"type":"message","id":"2c690d6e","parentId":"19939567","timestamp":"2026-03-27T05:01:17.326Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_n41TwQFdhySwwn3WrzKdsweQ","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.23-2 (7ffe7e4) — The only crab in your contacts you actually want to hear from. 🦞\n\nUsage: openclaw node [options] [command]\n\nRun and manage the headless node host service\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  help        Display help for command\n  install     Install the node host service (launchd/systemd/schtasks)\n  restart     Restart the node host service (launchd/systemd/schtasks)\n  run         Run the headless node host (foreground)\n  status      Show node host status\n  stop        Stop the node host service (launchd/systemd/schtasks)\n  uninstall   Uninstall the node host service (launchd/systemd/schtasks)\n\nExamples:\n  openclaw node run --host 127.0.0.1 --port 18789\n    Run the node host in the foreground.\n  openclaw node status\n    Check node host service status.\n  openclaw node install\n    Install the node host service.\n  openclaw node restart\n    Restart the installed node host service.\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/node"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1616,"aggregated":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.23-2 (7ffe7e4) — The only crab in your contacts you actually want to hear from. 🦞\n\nUsage: openclaw node [options] [command]\n\nRun and manage the headless node host service\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  help        Display help for command\n  install     Install the node host service (launchd/systemd/schtasks)\n  restart     Restart the node host service (launchd/systemd/schtasks)\n  run         Run the headless node host (foreground)\n  status      Show node host status\n  stop        Stop the node host service (launchd/systemd/schtasks)\n  uninstall   Uninstall the node host service (launchd/systemd/schtasks)\n\nExamples:\n  openclaw node run --host 127.0.0.1 --port 18789\n    Run the node host in the foreground.\n  openclaw node status\n    Check node host service status.\n  openclaw node install\n    Install the node host service.\n  openclaw node restart\n    Restart the installed node host service.\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/node","cwd":"/home/asus/.openclaw/workspaces/command"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774587677323}}
{"type":"message","id":"896d2e90","parentId":"2c690d6e","timestamp":"2026-03-27T05:01:22.974Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"node命令是管理节点主机服务的，可能不是用来启动特定代理的。也许需要看看openclaw agents是否有start命令？之前看到agents list，但没有agents start。可能代理是通过网关自动管理的？或者需要通过cron或系统事件来启动？让我检查一下openclaw system命令。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_Rv3oEbfln8NqCco1dC8YwPX6","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw system --help"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":944,"output":172,"cacheRead":72576,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":73692,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774587677327,"responseId":"b0dc2a7d-a958-47fe-8236-72ef39365d94"}}
{"type":"message","id":"614363a8","parentId":"896d2e90","timestamp":"2026-03-27T05:01:23.640Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_Rv3oEbfln8NqCco1dC8YwPX6","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.23-2 (7ffe7e4) — I speak fluent bash, mild sarcasm, and aggressive tab-completion energy.\n\nUsage: openclaw system [options] [command]\n\nSystem tools (events, heartbeat, presence)\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  event       Enqueue a system event and optionally trigger a heartbeat\n  heartbeat   Heartbeat controls\n  help        Display help for command\n  presence    List system presence entries\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/system"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":655,"aggregated":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.23-2 (7ffe7e4) — I speak fluent bash, mild sarcasm, and aggressive tab-completion energy.\n\nUsage: openclaw system [options] [command]\n\nSystem tools (events, heartbeat, presence)\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  event       Enqueue a system event and optionally trigger a heartbeat\n  heartbeat   Heartbeat controls\n  help        Display help for command\n  presence    List system presence entries\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/system","cwd":"/home/asus/.openclaw/workspaces/command"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774587683637}}
{"type":"message","id":"f22896d2","parentId":"614363a8","timestamp":"2026-03-27T05:01:42.195Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"也许可以通过system event来触发代理启动？或者更简单的方法：创建一个长期运行的子代理，设置很长的超时时间，并让它循环等待消息。这可能是最直接的解决方案。\n\n但首先，我需要向用户解释清楚。我将说明理想架构 vs 当前状态，然后提出两个具体选项：\n\n选项1：创建一个长期运行的offense子代理，标签为\"offense-persistent\"，它可以持续运行（例如24小时），并等待指令。我会记录其sessionKey，然后通过sessions_send发送任务。这模拟了独立的攻击者代理。\n\n选项2：尝试通过OpenClaw原生的代理启动机制（可能需要更复杂的配置），这可能更符合长远架构。\n\n考虑到用户可能想要简单有效的方案，我建议选项1。我会创建一个子代理，其任务是一个无限循环，等待消息。但更好的方法是：创建子代理，任务为\"等待指挥官指令\"，设置长超时，然后子代理会自动结束吗？不，我们需要子代理保持活动状态以接收sessions_send消息。子代理必须处于活动状态（status: running）才能接收消息。如果它的任务完成了，会话就结束了。所以我们需要一个永不完成的任务，比如一个循环，定期检查消息或等待信号。\n\n但sessions_send消息会作为新输入传递给子代理吗？我需要查一下OpenClaw的机制。当使用sessions_send时，目标会话必须处于活动状态，消息会作为新的用户输入传递。所以子代理需要处于等待输入的状态。\n\n我可以创建一个子代理，其任务为\"等待指令\"，然后它调用某个等待函数？但子代理是模型驱动的，它不能原地等待。也许可以在子代理内部使用exec sleep？不，这很混乱。\n\n或许OpenClaw的设计意图是：代理通过网关接收消息，当消息到来时启动代理实例。也就是说，offense代理应该配置为当特定消息到来时自动启动。这可能涉及路由绑定（routing bindings）。之前agents list显示offense有0个路由规则。也许需要添加路由绑定，使得发送到特定标签的消息自动启动offense代理。\n\n让我检查openclaw agents bindings。先看看openclaw agents bindings命令。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_WGRbOrFBZuZFzZJYG6MGWUel","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw agents bindings --help"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":300,"output":958,"cacheRead":73472,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":74730,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774587683641,"responseId":"ee5d971c-0db7-4455-982b-c44953e50096"}}
