{"type":"message","id":"15edd79c","parentId":"b0d720c2","timestamp":"2026-03-27T05:02:22.880Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_7lcUb5dkdlnP0GFusSTJz45e","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.23-2 (7ffe7e4) — If you're lost, run doctor; if you're brave, run prod; if you're wise, run tests.\n\nUsage: openclaw agents bind [options]\n\nAdd routing bindings for an agent\n\nOptions:\n  --agent <id>                  Agent id (defaults to current default agent)\n  --bind <channel[:accountId]>  Binding to add (repeatable). If omitted,\n                                accountId is resolved by channel defaults/hooks.\n                                (default: [])\n  -h, --help                    Display help for command\n  --json                        Output JSON summary (default: false)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1786,"aggregated":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.23-2 (7ffe7e4) — If you're lost, run doctor; if you're brave, run prod; if you're wise, run tests.\n\nUsage: openclaw agents bind [options]\n\nAdd routing bindings for an agent\n\nOptions:\n  --agent <id>                  Agent id (defaults to current default agent)\n  --bind <channel[:accountId]>  Binding to add (repeatable). If omitted,\n                                accountId is resolved by channel defaults/hooks.\n                                (default: [])\n  -h, --help                    Display help for command\n  --json                        Output JSON summary (default: false)","cwd":"/home/asus/.openclaw/workspaces/command"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774587742877}}
{"type":"message","id":"bdc70b41","parentId":"15edd79c","timestamp":"2026-03-27T05:04:32.773Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"bind命令看起来是针对频道的绑定，而不是基于标签的。可能路由绑定是将特定聊天频道（如Telegram、Discord）映射到代理。这似乎不是我们需要的。\n\n也许更简单的方法是：创建一个子代理，设置`mode: \"session\"`和`thread: true`，但之前失败了，因为\"no channel plugin registered subagent_spawning hooks\"。这可能是因为在webchat环境下不支持。\n\n那么，也许在OpenClaw的当前版本中，实现独立持久代理的正确方式是：使用`openclaw agent --agent offense --message ...`每次调用，就像我之前尝试的那样。但那次命令挂起了，可能是因为代理启动需要时间，或者需要传递`--deliver`参数？也许我应该用`--json`和超时参数再试一次。\n\n但用户想要的是持久会话，这样我可以随时发送任务。也许我可以创建一个后台进程，定期调用`openclaw agent`？或者用cron？\n\n在给出建议之前，我需要先向用户解释现状。让我组织一下语言。现在开始回复。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**架构现状 vs 理想目标**\n\n| 维度 | **理想架构** | **当前状态** |\n|------|--------------|--------------|\n| **指挥官** (command) | 分析、委托、不执行 | ✅ 符合（我正在运行） |\n| **攻击者** (offense) | 独立持久代理，随时接收任务并执行 | ❌ 未实现（仅配置，无活跃会话） |\n| **防御者** (defense) | 独立持久代理，负责观察与防御 | ❌ 未实现（仅配置） |\n| **通信方式** | 指挥官通过 `sessions_send` 直接向攻击者/防御者发送任务 | ❌ 无法实现（无接收会话） |\n| **执行单元** | 攻击者代理执行 | ⚠️ 由指挥官创建的子代理（subagent）代行 |\n\n**根本问题**  \n攻击者与防御者代理**已配置但未启动**，相当于“只有图纸，没有工人”。  \n我的临时解决方案是**自己扮演工头并临时雇人（子代理）**，这违背了“指挥官不执行”的原则。\n\n"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"error","timestamp":1774587742881,"responseId":"28178d86-b3fa-4191-8500-44fcc20a0e07","errorMessage":"terminated"}}
{"type":"message","id":"1222e0ec","parentId":"bdc70b41","timestamp":"2026-03-27T05:04:43.231Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"这看起来是绑定渠道（channel）和账户的，而不是绑定标签的。可能路由绑定是将特定聊天渠道的消息路由到特定代理。但我们需要的是在内部会话之间发送消息。\n\n或许更好的方法是使用cron创建一个持久会话。openclaw cron add可以创建一个定时任务，但也可以创建一次性的持久会话吗？cron job可以指定sessionTarget为\"session:offense\"，创建一个命名会话。然后我们可以向该会话发送消息。\n\n让我看看cron add的帮助。之前看到cron命令。现在检查一下。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_oo2YiGsqLngOSKSPmoqcha1U","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/asus/.npm-global/lib/node_modules/openclaw/docs/cron.md","limit":100}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":17,"output":300,"cacheRead":74688,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":75005,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774587874796,"responseId":"5393bcb2-3d72-4043-90eb-54116907e1d2"}}
