{"type":"message","id":"590981c4","parentId":"cd224083","timestamp":"2026-03-27T05:34:40.735Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户选择了C方案，也就是事件驱动任务队列。这确实有最大潜力，但实现难度较高。我需要先理解OpenClaw的事件系统和任务队列机制，然后设计一个可行的实施方案。\n\n首先，我得查阅OpenClaw关于系统事件（system event）、cron作业和钩子（hooks）的文档。用户之前提到了要“先把A架构搞出来”，但现在又选择了C方案。我需要明确：C方案是需要完全独立于A方案的全新架构，还是在A方案基础上叠加事件驱动层？用户可能希望直接构建事件驱动系统，但考虑到复杂度，也许还是需要先有基本的代理通信机制。\n\n让我先看看OpenClaw的system命令和cron功能。之前看到过`openclaw system event`和`openclaw cron`命令。事件驱动意味着指挥官发布事件，攻击者监听并处理。这可能需要配置cron作业来监听事件，或者使用钩子机制。\n\n我需要一个具体的计划：先研究OpenClaw事件系统，设计事件协议，然后实现一个简单的事件监听器，最后测试端到端流程。\n\n考虑到用户想要“发展潜力大”的方案，我应该设计一个可扩展的架构，即使初期实现简单。现在开始执行。首先查看system命令的帮助。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_WJODpZf47Y1IqyDa8A4TySet","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw system event --help"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":712,"output":563,"cacheRead":90432,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":91707,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774589666799,"responseId":"d8eec4f0-c6a9-4899-bc33-080294c0c78f"}}
{"type":"message","id":"049f7042","parentId":"590981c4","timestamp":"2026-03-27T05:34:41.482Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_WJODpZf47Y1IqyDa8A4TySet","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.23-2 (7ffe7e4) — Running on your hardware, reading your logs, judging nothing (mostly).\n\nUsage: openclaw system event [options]\n\nEnqueue a system event and optionally trigger a heartbeat\n\nOptions:\n  --expect-final   Wait for final response (agent) (default: false)\n  -h, --help       Display help for command\n  --json           Output JSON (default: false)\n  --mode <mode>    Wake mode (now|next-heartbeat) (default: \"next-heartbeat\")\n  --text <text>    System event text\n  --timeout <ms>   Timeout in ms (default: \"30000\")\n  --token <token>  Gateway token (if required)\n  --url <url>      Gateway WebSocket URL (defaults to gateway.remote.url when\n                   configured)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":734,"aggregated":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.23-2 (7ffe7e4) — Running on your hardware, reading your logs, judging nothing (mostly).\n\nUsage: openclaw system event [options]\n\nEnqueue a system event and optionally trigger a heartbeat\n\nOptions:\n  --expect-final   Wait for final response (agent) (default: false)\n  -h, --help       Display help for command\n  --json           Output JSON (default: false)\n  --mode <mode>    Wake mode (now|next-heartbeat) (default: \"next-heartbeat\")\n  --text <text>    System event text\n  --timeout <ms>   Timeout in ms (default: \"30000\")\n  --token <token>  Gateway token (if required)\n  --url <url>      Gateway WebSocket URL (defaults to gateway.remote.url when\n                   configured)","cwd":"/home/asus/.openclaw/workspaces/command"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774589681478}}
