{"type":"message","id":"7b3766b2","parentId":"a9939715","timestamp":"2026-03-27T05:34:47.171Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_N7xYrjlMwlw8mHpF5M4Dnzqe","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.23-2 (7ffe7e4) — I autocomplete your thoughts—just slower and with more API calls.\n\nUsage: openclaw cron [options] [command]\n\nManage cron jobs (via Gateway)\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  add         Add a cron job\n  disable     Disable a cron job\n  edit        Edit a cron job (patch fields)\n  enable      Enable a cron job\n  help        Display help for command\n  list        List cron jobs\n  rm          Remove a cron job\n  run         Run a cron job now (debug)\n  runs        Show cron run history (JSONL-backed)\n  status      Show cron scheduler status\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/cron\nUpgrade tip: run `openclaw doctor --fix` to normalize legacy cron job storage."}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":680,"aggregated":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.23-2 (7ffe7e4) — I autocomplete your thoughts—just slower and with more API calls.\n\nUsage: openclaw cron [options] [command]\n\nManage cron jobs (via Gateway)\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  add         Add a cron job\n  disable     Disable a cron job\n  edit        Edit a cron job (patch fields)\n  enable      Enable a cron job\n  help        Display help for command\n  list        List cron jobs\n  rm          Remove a cron job\n  run         Run a cron job now (debug)\n  runs        Show cron run history (JSONL-backed)\n  status      Show cron scheduler status\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/cron\nUpgrade tip: run `openclaw doctor --fix` to normalize legacy cron job storage.","cwd":"/home/asus/.openclaw/workspaces/command"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774589687167}}
{"type":"message","id":"92d85b59","parentId":"7b3766b2","timestamp":"2026-03-27T05:34:57.134Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"查看cron add的帮助，了解如何创建任务。同时需要理解OpenClaw的钩子（hooks）系统。不过，事件驱动方案可能涉及以下组件：\n\n1. 指挥官发布系统事件（`openclaw system event --text \"任务描述\"`）\n2. 攻击者代理监听事件并处理。监听可以通过cron作业定期轮询，或者通过网关的WebSocket订阅事件。\n3. 攻击者处理完任务后，将结果通过某种方式返回给指挥官（可能是另一个系统事件，或者写入共享文件，或者通过sessions_send）。\n\n我需要研究OpenClaw是否有事件订阅机制。如果没有，可能需要使用cron作业定期检查事件队列。\n\n让我先看看cron add的帮助，了解如何创建触发代理运行的cron作业。同时查看hooks命令。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_RijZi0nTcnnnmObws7xsZqCi","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw cron add --help"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":285,"output":383,"cacheRead":91648,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":92316,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774589687172,"responseId":"2d981053-5266-4f1c-a3d2-800d39579d1d"}}
{"type":"message","id":"e22a7e67","parentId":"92d85b59","timestamp":"2026-03-27T05:34:57.905Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_RijZi0nTcnnnmObws7xsZqCi","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.23-2 (7ffe7e4) — Less clicking, more shipping, fewer \"where did that file go\" moments.\n\nUsage: openclaw cron add|create [options]\n\nAdd a cron job\n\nOptions:\n  --account <id>         Channel account id for delivery (multi-account setups)\n  --agent <id>           Agent id for this job\n  --announce             Announce summary to a chat (subagent-style) (default:\n                         false)\n  --at <when>            Run once at time (ISO with offset, or +duration). Use\n                         --tz for offset-less datetimes\n  --best-effort-deliver  Do not fail the job if delivery fails (default: false)\n  --channel <channel>    Delivery channel (last) (default: \"last\")\n  --cron <expr>          Cron expression (5-field or 6-field with seconds)\n  --delete-after-run     Delete one-shot job after it succeeds (default: false)\n  --deliver              Deprecated (use --announce). Announces a summary to a\n                         chat.\n  --description <text>   Optional description\n  --disabled             Create job disabled (default: false)\n  --every <duration>     Run every duration (e.g. 10m, 1h)\n  --exact                Disable cron staggering (set stagger to 0) (default:\n                         false)\n  --expect-final         Wait for final response (agent) (default: false)\n  -h, --help             Display help for command\n  --json                 Output JSON (default: false)\n  --keep-after-run       Keep one-shot job after it succeeds (default: false)\n  --light-context        Use lightweight bootstrap context for agent jobs\n                         (default: false)\n  --message <text>       Agent message payload\n  --model <model>        Model override for agent jobs (provider/model or alias)\n  --name <name>          Job name\n  --no-deliver           Disable announce delivery and skip main-session summary\n  --session <target>     Session target (main|isolated)\n  --session-key <key>    Session key for job routing (e.g.\n                         agent:my-agent:my-session)\n  --stagger <duration>   Cron stagger window (e.g. 30s, 5m)\n  --system-event <text>  System event payload (main session)\n  --thinking <level>     Thinking level for agent jobs\n                         (off|minimal|low|medium|high|xhigh)\n  --timeout <ms>         Timeout in ms (default: \"30000\")\n  --timeout-seconds <n>  Timeout seconds for agent jobs\n  --to <dest>            Delivery destination (E.164, Telegram chatId, or\n                         Discord channel/user)\n  --token <token>        Gateway token (if required)\n  --tz <iana>            Timezone for cron expressions (IANA) (default: \"\")\n  --url <url>            Gateway WebSocket URL (defaults to gateway.remote.url\n                         when configured)\n  --wake <mode>          Wake mode (now|next-heartbeat) (default: \"now\")"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":759,"aggregated":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.23-2 (7ffe7e4) — Less clicking, more shipping, fewer \"where did that file go\" moments.\n\nUsage: openclaw cron add|create [options]\n\nAdd a cron job\n\nOptions:\n  --account <id>         Channel account id for delivery (multi-account setups)\n  --agent <id>           Agent id for this job\n  --announce             Announce summary to a chat (subagent-style) (default:\n                         false)\n  --at <when>            Run once at time (ISO with offset, or +duration). Use\n                         --tz for offset-less datetimes\n  --best-effort-deliver  Do not fail the job if delivery fails (default: false)\n  --channel <channel>    Delivery channel (last) (default: \"last\")\n  --cron <expr>          Cron expression (5-field or 6-field with seconds)\n  --delete-after-run     Delete one-shot job after it succeeds (default: false)\n  --deliver              Deprecated (use --announce). Announces a summary to a\n                         chat.\n  --description <text>   Optional description\n  --disabled             Create job disabled (default: false)\n  --every <duration>     Run every duration (e.g. 10m, 1h)\n  --exact                Disable cron staggering (set stagger to 0) (default:\n                         false)\n  --expect-final         Wait for final response (agent) (default: false)\n  -h, --help             Display help for command\n  --json                 Output JSON (default: false)\n  --keep-after-run       Keep one-shot job after it succeeds (default: false)\n  --light-context        Use lightweight bootstrap context for agent jobs\n                         (default: false)\n  --message <text>       Agent message payload\n  --model <model>        Model override for agent jobs (provider/model or alias)\n  --name <name>          Job name\n  --no-deliver           Disable announce delivery and skip main-session summary\n  --session <target>     Session target (main|isolated)\n  --session-key <key>    Session key for job routing (e.g.\n                         agent:my-agent:my-session)\n  --stagger <duration>   Cron stagger window (e.g. 30s, 5m)\n  --system-event <text>  System event payload (main session)\n  --thinking <level>     Thinking level for agent jobs\n                         (off|minimal|low|medium|high|xhigh)\n  --timeout <ms>         Timeout in ms (default: \"30000\")\n  --timeout-seconds <n>  Timeout seconds for agent jobs\n  --to <dest>            Delivery destination (E.164, Telegram chatId, or\n                         Discord channel/user)\n  --token <token>        Gateway token (if required)\n  --tz <iana>            Timezone for cron expressions (IANA) (default: \"\")\n  --url <url>            Gateway WebSocket URL (defaults to gateway.remote.url\n                         when configured)\n  --wake <mode>          Wake mode (now|next-heartbeat) (default: \"now\")","cwd":"/home/asus/.openclaw/workspaces/command"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774589697902}}
{"type":"message","id":"07db394d","parentId":"e22a7e67","timestamp":"2026-03-27T05:35:25.599Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"很好！cron add 支持 `--system-event <text>` 和 `--message <text>`。我可以创建一个cron作业，定期检查事件队列，或者直接创建响应系统事件的作业。\n\n但事件驱动架构需要解决几个问题：\n1. **事件存储**：如何存储待处理的任务事件？\n2. **事件分发**：如何将事件分发给正确的代理？\n3. **结果返回**：代理如何处理结果？\n\n一个简单的设计：\n- 使用一个共享文件作为事件队列（例如 `~/.openclaw/events/tasks.jsonl`）。\n- 指挥官写入事件（任务描述、目标代理、优先级等）。\n- 攻击者代理通过cron作业定期读取并处理事件。\n- 处理完成后，攻击者将结果写入另一个文件，或通过sessions_send发送给指挥官。\n\n但更符合OpenClaw哲学的方式可能是：\n- 指挥官发布系统事件（`openclaw system event --text \"offense:scan-cmcc\"`）。\n- 配置一个cron作业，监听系统事件并触发攻击者代理。\n\n然而，系统事件默认是发送到主会话（main session）的。我需要了解如何让系统事件触发特定代理。\n\n让我看看hooks命令。先检查是否有hooks子命令。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_sLkDFxoQZjhBfY3xweafiM4e","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw hooks --help"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":82411,"output":576,"cacheRead":9856,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":92843,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774589697907,"responseId":"85d48e8a-0e2b-4d9c-b408-882f8f1dae09"}}
{"type":"message","id":"0fffc17d","parentId":"07db394d","timestamp":"2026-03-27T05:35:27.199Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_sLkDFxoQZjhBfY3xweafiM4e","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.23-2 (7ffe7e4) — I can't fix your code taste, but I can fix your build and your backlog.\n\nUsage: openclaw hooks [options] [command]\n\nManage internal agent hooks\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  check       Check hooks eligibility status\n  disable     Disable a hook\n  enable      Enable a hook\n  info        Show detailed information about a hook\n  install     Deprecated: install a hook pack via `openclaw plugins install`\n  list        List all hooks\n  update      Deprecated: update hook packs via `openclaw plugins update`\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/hooks"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1586,"aggregated":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.23-2 (7ffe7e4) — I can't fix your code taste, but I can fix your build and your backlog.\n\nUsage: openclaw hooks [options] [command]\n\nManage internal agent hooks\n\nOptions:\n  -h, --help  Display help for command\n\nCommands:\n  check       Check hooks eligibility status\n  disable     Disable a hook\n  enable      Enable a hook\n  info        Show detailed information about a hook\n  install     Deprecated: install a hook pack via `openclaw plugins install`\n  list        List all hooks\n  update      Deprecated: update hook packs via `openclaw plugins update`\n\nDocs: https://docs.openclaw.ai/cli/hooks","cwd":"/home/asus/.openclaw/workspaces/command"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774589727196}}
{"type":"message","id":"a55f841a","parentId":"0fffc17d","timestamp":"2026-03-27T05:35:47.210Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"看看hooks list。可能需要查看现有钩子，了解如何创建自定义钩子。不过这可能涉及插件开发，比较复杂。\n\n考虑到时间，也许可以先实现一个简化版的事件驱动系统：使用cron作业定期运行攻击者代理，代理检查任务队列并处理。指挥官通过写入队列文件来发布任务。\n\n但这需要文件共享，而且攻击者需要访问指挥官工作区的文件。也许可以放在共享目录，比如 `/home/asus/.openclaw/events/`。\n\n让我先设计一个简单可行的事件驱动架构，然后向用户汇报计划。现在整理思路。\n\n用户选择了C方案，这意味着我需要设计一个事件驱动任务队列系统。这个系统应该有以下组件：\n\n1. **事件队列**：存储待处理任务。\n2. **事件发布者**（指挥官）：发布任务事件。\n3. **事件消费者**（攻击者/防御者）：监听并处理事件。\n4. **结果处理器**：收集处理结果并反馈给指挥官。\n\n实现方案选项：\n- **方案C1**：使用文件系统作为队列（JSONL文件），cron作业定期触发代理读取。\n- **方案C2**：使用系统事件，配置钩子或cron作业监听事件并触发代理。\n- **方案C3**：使用数据库或消息队列（如Redis），但需要额外安装。\n\n考虑到简单性和与OpenClaw的集成，**方案C2**可能更合适，但需要深入理解系统事件的工作机制。\n\n让我先看看系统事件是如何工作的。可以创建一个测试系统事件，看看它去哪里了。但首先，我需要制定一个详细的C方案实施计划。\n\n用户说“C方案”，我需要提供具体的计划，然后逐步执行。我应该先研究，然后提出分阶段计划。\n\n现在开始研究：创建一个系统事件，观察其行为。先看看当前有哪些cron作业。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_sh3VshuV6B86uv8pAfc3PnEb","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw cron list"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":14017,"output":801,"cacheRead":78144,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":92962,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774589727200,"responseId":"d1b8ed07-6fa4-4c76-b223-c94be3536174"}}
