{"type":"message","id":"3e03deb9","parentId":"296a2c97","timestamp":"2026-03-27T08:19:48.591Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"目录不存在，需要创建。现在开始设计短期落地计划。\n\n我将分为三个子阶段：\n1. 基础设施搭建（目录、文件结构、基本脚本）\n2. 单个任务闭环测试（从发布到反馈）\n3. 扩展为多类别攻击者（可选，短期可做基础）\n\n需要确保攻击者能执行命令，可以测试一下 sudo 密码是否有效。用简单的命令测试。但不要运行耗时任务。现在先执行一个快速测试。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_QX6kt6mmNfFy8AcCKqM3hqTz","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo '666' | sudo -S whoami 2>&1 | head -1"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":84818,"output":256,"cacheRead":11392,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":96466,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774599556613,"responseId":"e12277c3-99e7-4c2a-9fd4-93bdd14aa40e"}}
