{"type":"message","id":"d42ea989","parentId":"3dcd4b11","timestamp":"2026-03-27T08:53:02.628Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"很好！wlan1 已经是监控模式（type monitor），频道3。这意味着可以直接用于扫描。\n\n现在，需要修改 `consume.py` 中的 `execute_scan_cmcc` 函数，使其运行真实的 `airodump-ng` 命令。但要注意，airodump-ng 会持续运行直到手动停止。我们需要指定扫描持续时间（比如10秒），然后捕获输出。可以使用 `timeout` 命令。同时，需要将输出保存到临时文件，然后解析。\n\n然而，解析 airodump-ng 的输出比较复杂。我们可以先简化：捕获原始输出，作为原始数据存储。以后可以逐步改进解析。\n\n另外，需要考虑扫描多个频道，因为 CMCC 热点可能在不同频道。可以扫描频道1-13。\n\n现在，修改 `consume.py`。首先备份原文件。然后编辑。使用 edit 工具替换 `execute_scan_cmcc` 函数。同时，可能需要添加一个辅助函数来运行命令并捕获输出。\n\n另外，需要考虑 sudo 密码。消费者脚本将以攻击者代理身份运行，但 cron 作业是以当前用户（asus）运行。我们需要在脚本中处理 sudo 密码。可以使用 `echo '666' | sudo -S` 方式。但要注意，sudo 可能需要 tty。可以在 sudoers 中配置免密码，但暂时用密码方式。\n\n此外，需要处理命令超时和错误。\n\n现在，开始修改。首先读取当前 `consume.py` 内容，然后替换相应部分。使用 edit 工具。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_FPD3UbsQXaftxK9m4Bs2nLIs","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/asus/.openclaw/events/consume.py","offset":80,"limit":50}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":286,"output":724,"cacheRead":83136,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":84146,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774601554946,"responseId":"5b5f6db2-90f5-4149-9b7f-c5b872937bb6"}}
{"type":"message","id":"7dd2113d","parentId":"d42ea989","timestamp":"2026-03-27T08:53:02.680Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_FPD3UbsQXaftxK9m4Bs2nLIs","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    interface = params.get(\"interface\", \"wlan1\")\n    duration = params.get(\"duration\", 10)\n    # 这里应调用实际的 airodump-ng 命令，但为了测试先模拟\n    print(f\"模拟扫描: interface={interface}, duration={duration}s\")\n    time.sleep(2)\n    return {\n        \"scanResults\": [\n            {\"bssid\": \"AA:BB:CC:DD:EE:FF\", \"ssid\": \"CMCC\", \"channel\": 6},\n            {\"bssid\": \"11:22:33:44:55:66\", \"ssid\": \"CMCC-WEB\", \"channel\": 11}\n        ],\n        \"success\": True\n    }\n\ndef handle_event(event):\n    \"\"\"处理单个事件\"\"\"\n    event_id = event[\"id\"]\n    task = event[\"task\"]\n    params = event.get(\"params\", {})\n    \n    print(f\"处理事件 {event_id}: task={task}\")\n    \n    # 根据任务类型执行\n    if task == \"ping\":\n        result = execute_ping(params)\n    elif task == \"scan-cmcc\":\n        result = execute_scan_cmcc(params)\n    else:\n        result = {\"error\": f\"未知任务: {task}\", \"success\": False}\n    \n    # 构建原始数据\n    raw_data = {\n        \"task\": task,\n        \"params\": params,\n        \"executionResult\": result\n    }\n    \n    metadata = {\n        \"duration\": 2,  # 模拟执行时间\n        \"toolsUsed\": [\"airodump-ng\"] if task == \"scan-cmcc\" else []\n    }\n    \n    status = \"completed\" if result.get(\"success\") else \"failed\"\n    write_result(event_id, status, raw_data, metadata)\n    return status\n\ndef main():\n    # 文件锁，避免并发消费\n    lock_file = TASKS_FILE.with_suffix(\".lock\")\n    try:\n        with open(lock_file, \"w\") as lock:\n\n[59 more lines in file. Use offset=130 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774601582676}}
