{"type":"message","id":"a58f398a","parentId":"c737e843","timestamp":"2026-03-27T08:53:25.113Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_jqSFVldfX3bbSBEAeGu3DJif","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"    return {\n        \"output\": f\"Ping response: {message}\",\n        \"success\": True\n    }\n\ndef execute_scan_cmcc(params):\n    \"\"\"执行 CMCC 扫描任务\"\"\"\n    interface = params.get(\"interface\", \"wlan1\")\n    duration = params.get(\"duration\", 10)\n    # 这里应调用实际的 airodump-ng 命令，但为了测试先模拟\n    print(f\"模拟扫描: interface={interface}, duration={duration}s\")\n    time.sleep(2)\n    return {\n        \"scanResults\": [\n            {\"bssid\": \"AA:BB:CC:DD:EE:FF\", \"ssid\": \"CMCC\", \"channel\": 6},\n            {\"bssid\": \"11:22:33:44:55:66\", \"ssid\": \"CMCC-WEB\", \"channel\": 11}\n        ],\n        \"success\": True\n    }\n\n\n[96 more lines in file. Use offset=93 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774601605110}}
{"type":"message","id":"1e7f0bdc","parentId":"a58f398a","timestamp":"2026-03-27T08:54:17.503Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在，用新的实现替换这个函数。新函数将运行真实的 airodump-ng。注意：需要导入 subprocess 并处理 sudo 密码。使用 `echo '666' | sudo -S timeout ${duration} airodump-ng -w /tmp/scan-${event_id} -o csv ${interface}`。但 airodump-ng 会持续运行直到被停止。使用 `timeout` 命令限制时间。输出格式可以是 csv。然后读取 CSV 文件并解析。但解析 CSV 较复杂；可以先保存原始输出和 CSV 文件路径作为结果。\n\n另外，需要确保临时文件唯一，避免冲突。使用事件 ID 作为文件名的一部分。\n\n现在，编辑。首先，确保我们有权访问 subprocess 模块（已导入）。现在替换。使用 edit 工具。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_TBW4MSaiIrBIt0PtAGIZddez","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/asus/.openclaw/events/consume.py","oldText":"def execute_scan_cmcc(params):\n    \"\"\"执行 CMCC 扫描任务\"\"\"\n    interface = params.get(\"interface\", \"wlan1\")\n    duration = params.get(\"duration\", 10)\n    # 这里应调用实际的 airodump-ng 命令，但为了测试先模拟\n    print(f\"模拟扫描: interface={interface}, duration={duration}s\")\n    time.sleep(2)\n    return {\n        \"scanResults\": [\n            {\"bssid\": \"AA:BB:CC:DD:EE:FF\", \"ssid\": \"CMCC\", \"channel\": 6},\n            {\"bssid\": \"11:22:33:44:55:66\", \"ssid\": \"CMCC-WEB\", \"channel\": 11}\n        ],\n        \"success\": True\n    }","newText":"def execute_scan_cmcc(params):\n    \"\"\"执行 CMCC 扫描任务 - 真实 airodump-ng 扫描\"\"\"\n    interface = params.get(\"interface\", \"wlan1\")\n    duration = params.get(\"duration\", 30)  # 默认扫描30秒\n    channels = params.get(\"channels\", \"1-13\")  # 扫描频道范围\n    \n    import subprocess, tempfile, os, time, csv, json\n    \n    print(f\"开始真实扫描: interface={interface}, duration={duration}s, channels={channels}\")\n    \n    # 创建临时文件前缀\n    tmp_prefix = f\"/tmp/scan_{int(time.time())}_{os.getpid()}\"\n    csv_file = f\"{tmp_prefix}-01.csv\"\n    \n    # 构建命令: 使用 timeout 限制时长，扫描指定频道，输出 CSV\n    cmd = f\"timeout {duration} sudo airodump-ng -w {tmp_prefix} -o csv --channel {channels} {interface}\"\n    \n    try:\n        # 执行扫描 (需要 sudo 密码，通过管道传递)\n        proc = subprocess.Popen(\n            cmd,\n            shell=True,\n            stdin=subprocess.PIPE,\n            stdout=subprocess.PIPE,\n            stderr=subprocess.PIPE,\n            text=True\n        )\n        # 提供 sudo 密码（如果配置了免密码则不需要）\n        stdout, stderr = proc.communicate(input='666\\n')\n        exit_code = proc.wait()\n        \n        raw_output = stdout + \"\\n\" + stderr\n        \n        # 读取 CSV 文件（如果生成）\n        scan_results = []\n        if os.path.exists(csv_file):\n            with open(csv_file, 'r', encoding='utf-8', errors='ignore') as f:\n                reader = csv.reader(f)\n                rows = list(reader)\n                # 简单解析：跳过前几行，提取 BSSID, SSID, CH 等\n                for row in rows:\n                    if len(row) >= 14 and row[0].strip():  # BSSID 列非空\n                        bssid = row[0].strip()\n                        ssid = row[13].strip() if len(row) > 13 else ''\n                        channel = row[3].strip() if len(row) > 3 else ''\n                        if ssid and ('CMCC' in ssid.upper() or 'CHINAMOBILE' in ssid.upper()):\n                            scan_results.append({\n                                \"bssid\": bssid,\n                                \"ssid\": ssid,\n                                \"channel\": channel,\n                                \"rssi\": row[8].strip() if len(row) > 8 else ''\n                            })\n        \n        # 清理临时文件（可选保留供调试）\n        # os.remove(csv_file) if os.path.exists(csv_file) else None\n        \n        return {\n            \"scanResults\": scan_results,\n            \"rawOutput\": raw_output[:5000],  # 限制长度\n            \"csvFile\": csv_file if os.path.exists(csv_file) else None,\n            \"success\": True,\n            \"exitCode\": exit_code\n        }\n    \n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"扫描出错: {e}\")\n        return {\n            \"error\": str(e),\n            \"success\": False\n        }"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":453,"output":1311,"cacheRead":84224,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":85988,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774601605114,"responseId":"ddf2f199-7361-4d4f-9137-c4c10d80984b"}}
