{"type":"message","id":"dbc731a2","parentId":"629c1135","timestamp":"2026-03-27T09:36:00.633Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_BxfGlas1aq3VJLYp9Y5Z0FIP","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\ndef handle_event(event):\n    \"\"\"处理单个事件\"\"\"\n    event_id = event[\"id\"]\n    task = event[\"task\"]\n    params = event.get(\"params\", {})\n    \n    print(f\"处理事件 {event_id}: task={task}\")\n    \n    # 根据任务类型执行\n    if task == \"ping\":\n        result = execute_ping(params)\n    elif task == \"scan-cmcc\":\n        result = execute_scan_cmcc(params)\n    else:\n        result = {\"error\": f\"未知任务: {task}\", \"success\": False}\n    \n    # 构建原始数据\n    raw_data = {\n        \"task\": task,\n        \"params\": params,\n        \"executionResult\": result\n    }\n    \n    metadata = {\n        \"duration\": 2,  # 模拟执行时间\n        \"toolsUsed\": [\"airodump-ng\"] if task == \"scan-cmcc\" else []\n    }\n    \n    status = \"completed\" if result.get(\"success\") else \"failed\"\n    write_result(event_id, status, raw_data, metadata)\n    return status\n\ndef main():\n    # 文件锁，避免并发消费\n    lock_file = TASKS_FILE.with_suffix(\".lock\")\n    try:\n        with open(lock_file, \"w\") as lock:\n            fcntl.flock(lock, fcntl.LOCK_EX | fcntl.LOCK_NB)\n            \n            events = load_events()\n            pending_events = [e for e in events if e[\"status\"] == \"pending\"]\n            \n            if not pending_events:\n                print(\"无待处理事件\")\n                return\n            \n            # 每次只处理一个事件（避免阻塞）\n            event = pending_events[0]\n            event_id = event[\"id\"]\n\n[47 more lines in file. Use offset=290 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1774604160629}}
{"type":"message","id":"01bfd8ef","parentId":"dbc731a2","timestamp":"2026-03-27T09:36:52.552Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"找到了`handle_event`函数。现在我需要修改它，首先尝试API调用，如果失败则回退到本地执行。同时，我需要更新`metadata`中的`toolsUsed`字段，以反映是否使用了API。\n\n让我修改`handle_event`函数。首先，我需要决定何时使用API。如果事件有`category`字段，并且API可用且配置了该类别，则尝试API调用。否则，使用本地执行。\n\n修改`handle_event`函数。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_R36t4B3wnlRMu4o1pPdEnkAt","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/asus/.openclaw/events/consume.py","oldText":"def handle_event(event):\n    \"\"\"处理单个事件\"\"\"\n    event_id = event[\"id\"]\n    task = event[\"task\"]\n    params = event.get(\"params\", {})\n    \n    print(f\"处理事件 {event_id}: task={task}\")\n    \n    # 根据任务类型执行\n    if task == \"ping\":\n        result = execute_ping(params)\n    elif task == \"scan-cmcc\":\n        result = execute_scan_cmcc(params)\n    else:\n        result = {\"error\": f\"未知任务: {task}\", \"success\": False}\n    \n    # 构建原始数据\n    raw_data = {\n        \"task\": task,\n        \"params\": params,\n        \"executionResult\": result\n    }\n    \n    metadata = {\n        \"duration\": 2,  # 模拟执行时间\n        \"toolsUsed\": [\"airodump-ng\"] if task == \"scan-cmcc\" else []\n    }\n    \n    status = \"completed\" if result.get(\"success\") else \"failed\"\n    write_result(event_id, status, raw_data, metadata)\n    return status","newText":"def handle_event(event):\n    \"\"\"处理单个事件\"\"\"\n    event_id = event[\"id\"]\n    task = event[\"task\"]\n    params = event.get(\"params\", {})\n    category = event.get(\"category\")\n    \n    print(f\"处理事件 {event_id}: task={task}, category={category}\")\n    \n    result = None\n    api_used = False\n    \n    # 如果指定了类别且 API 可用，尝试调用 API\n    if category and REQUESTS_AVAILABLE:\n        api_result = call_attack_api(event)\n        if api_result is not None:\n            result = api_result\n            api_used = True\n            print(f\"使用 API 处理事件 {event_id} 成功\")\n        else:\n            print(f\"API 调用失败，回退到本地执行\")\n    \n    # 如果 API 未使用或失败，使用本地执行\n    if result is None:\n        if task == \"ping\":\n            result = execute_ping(params)\n        elif task == \"scan-cmcc\":\n            result = execute_scan_cmcc(params)\n        else:\n            result = {\"error\": f\"未知任务: {task}\", \"success\": False}\n    \n    # 构建原始数据\n    raw_data = {\n        \"task\": task,\n        \"params\": params,\n        \"executionResult\": result,\n        \"apiUsed\": api_used,\n        \"category\": category\n    }\n    \n    # 估计执行时间（实际应测量，这里简化）\n    duration = 2 if task == \"ping\" else 5 if task == \"scan-cmcc\" else 1\n    \n    metadata = {\n        \"duration\": duration,\n        \"toolsUsed\": [\"airodump-ng\"] if task == \"scan-cmcc\" else [],\n        \"apiUsed\": api_used\n    }\n    \n    status = \"completed\" if result.get(\"success\") else \"failed\"\n    write_result(event_id, status, raw_data, metadata)\n    return status"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":70007,"output":929,"cacheRead":27008,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":97944,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774604160634,"responseId":"49d41c8a-f6a0-4257-aad5-3141811aa989"}}
