{"type":"message","id":"2dbd09cb","parentId":"b6acc588","timestamp":"2026-03-27T10:07:51.584Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我看到问题了！事件 `7cd0a237-eb34-468e-b818-968436294726` 的状态是 `processing` 而不是 `pending`。消费者只处理 `pending` 状态的事件。这意味着事件可能被锁定在 `processing` 状态了，可能因为之前的处理进程崩溃了。\n\n我需要检查消费者是否正确地更新了状态。事件有 `statusHistory` 显示它在 `2026-03-27T09:38:43.428092+00:00` 进入了 `processing` 状态，但没有 `completed` 记录。\n\n这表明消费者在处理过程中崩溃了，没有将状态更新回 `completed` 或 `failed`。这可能是由于文件锁问题或进程被终止。\n\n我需要修复这个问题：要么将状态重置为 `pending` 以重新处理，要么检查是否有部分结果。\n\n让我先检查是否有对应的结果记录。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_h0pGG54g7b3fs4mkyzkco96r","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/asus/.openclaw/events && grep -n '\"7cd0a237-eb34-468e-b818-968436294726\"' results.jsonl"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":62712,"output":448,"cacheRead":36032,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":99192,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774606040175,"responseId":"0c07b434-085f-486a-ac6e-ec6b8de0fcf6"}}
