{"type":"message","id":"ae3a115b","parentId":"36446a03","timestamp":"2026-03-27T10:08:06.903Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"没有结果记录。所以事件卡在 `processing` 状态了。我需要修改事件状态回 `pending` 以重新处理。\n\n但首先，我需要理解为什么消费者会崩溃。可能的原因包括：\n1. API调用失败（因为端点未配置）导致异常。\n2. 文件锁问题。\n3. 超时或被杀死。\n\n让我查看消费者日志中是否有相关错误。先检查消费者日志的最后几行。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_wv0vL1rVCetd1X4fCtai1onB","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/asus/.openclaw/events && tail -20 consumer.log"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":344,"output":235,"cacheRead":98688,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":99267,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774606071639,"responseId":"b5dca876-a3f5-48f1-8d1d-a42eeb92cbb4"}}
