{"type":"message","id":"fc2d468d","parentId":"ef94191e","timestamp":"2026-03-27T10:08:30.024Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"日志只显示“无待处理事件”。这说明消费者确实没有看到 `pending` 事件。但事件状态是 `processing`，所以消费者可能认为它正在被处理。\n\n现在，关于API端点的问题。用户提供了两个URL：\n1. `https://api.deepseek.com/beta`\n2. `https://api.deepseek.com/chat/completions`\n\n我需要弄清楚哪个是正确的。根据DeepSeek的文档，标准API端点是 `https://api.deepseek.com/chat/completions`。`/beta` 路径可能是贝塔版本的基础路径，实际的聊天补全端点可能是 `https://api.deepseek.com/beta/chat/completions`。\n\n让我检查是否有 `requests` 库，然后发送一个测试请求来验证端点。但首先，我需要回答用户的问题并更新配置。\n\n我需要向用户解释：\n- `https://api.deepseek.com/chat/completions` 是标准聊天补全端点。\n- `https://api.deepseek.com/beta` 可能是贝塔版本的基础URL，实际端点可能需要附加路径。\n\n让我先更新 `apis.json`，将 `base_url` 设置为 `https://api.deepseek.com/beta`，并保留 `endpoint` 为 `/chat/completions`。这样完整URL就是 `https://api.deepseek.com/beta/chat/completions`。\n\n但首先，我需要修复卡住的事件。让我将状态重置为 `pending`。我将编辑tasks.jsonl文件。让我先备份。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_KMVo1ssqJtSAGjlLd9I6mGI2","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/asus/.openclaw/events/tasks.jsonl","offset":3,"limit":2}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":287,"output":712,"cacheRead":99008,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":100007,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774606086947,"responseId":"45d5a3cf-c5bb-4cc0-bf13-db2d6621971f"}}
