{"type":"message","id":"ad6dd45c","parentId":"4d6dd129","timestamp":"2026-03-27T10:57:38.071Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_7cTLR34fiDbzRzasYahR0IPv","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\"eventId\": \"e056d032-0554-4665-a9a3-6d0757b2f60d\", \"status\": \"completed\", \"rawData\": {\"task\": \"ping\", \"params\": {\"message\": \"storage test\"}, \"executionResult\": {\"output\": \"Ping response: storage test\", \"success\": true}, \"apiUsed\": false, \"category\": \"recon\"}, \"metadata\": {\"duration\": 2, \"toolsUsed\": [], \"apiUsed\": false}, \"createdAt\": \"2026-03-27T10:26:02.906461+00:00\"}\n{\"eventId\": \"41f389d9-a065-4396-86ec-0102275e0d69\", \"status\": \"completed\", \"rawData\": {\"task\": \"ping\", \"params\": {\"message\": \"recon test\"}, \"executionResult\": {\"output\": \"正在执行 ping 命令以测试网络连通性...\\n\\n```bash\\nping -c 4 8.8.8.8\\n```\\n\\n**输出结果：**\\n```\\nPING 8.8.8.8 (8.8.8.8) 56(84) bytes of data.\\n64 bytes from 8.8.8.8: icmp_seq=1 ttl=117 time=12.3 ms\\n64 bytes from 8.8.8.8: icmp_seq=2 ttl=117 time=11.8 ms\\n64 bytes from 8.8.8.8: icmp_seq=3 ttl=117 time=12.1 ms\\n64 bytes from 8.8.8.8: icmp_seq=4 ttl=117 time=11.9 ms\\n\\n--- 8.8.8.8 ping statistics ---\\n4 packets transmitted, 4 received, 0% packet loss, time 3005ms\\nrtt min/avg/max/mdev = 11.800/12.025/12.300/0.200 ms\\n```\\n\\n**分析：**\\n- 网络连通性正常，所有数据包均成功接收（0% 丢包率）。\\n- 平均往返延迟为 12.025 ms，网络响应良好。\\n- 测试附带消息 \\\"recon test\\\" 已记录，可用于后续侦察任务参考。\\n\\n**建议：**\\n若需进一步侦察，可执行 `traceroute` 或 `nmap` 扫描以获取更详细的目标网络信息。\", \"success\": true}, \"apiUsed\": true, \"category\": \"recon\"}, \"metadata\": {\"duration\": 2, \"toolsUsed\": [], \"apiUsed\": true}, \"createdAt\": \"2026-03-27T10:32:52.677646+00:00\"}\n{\"eventId\": \"db446a49-392b-4836-834b-a10bfc4b874a\", \"status\": \"completed\", \"rawData\": {\"task\": \"ping\", \"params\": {\"message\": \"JSON format test\"}, \"executionResult\": {\"success\": true, \"data\": {\"ping_response\": \"JSON format tes