{"type":"message","id":"1b99596a","parentId":"d061f262","timestamp":"2026-03-27T11:11:50.327Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"队列是空的，很好。现在开始测试剩余类别。我需要发布4个测试事件，分别对应web、internal、exploit、social。使用ping任务，带不同的测试消息，以便区分。\n\n首先发布web类别任务。然后internal，再exploit，最后social。之后手动运行消费者处理。为了避免cron干扰，我先检查cron状态，但手动运行consumer应该没问题。实际上cron每分钟运行一次，可能会与我同时处理，但文件锁会防止冲突。\n\n开始执行。先暂停cron吗？暂时不用，因为队列是空的，而且文件锁会处理并发。直接发布任务吧。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_K5fusN9b1oUY9OWFHPpxgFLZ","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /home/asus/.openclaw/events && python3 publish.py --type test --task ping --category web --params '{\"message\":\"web category test\"}'"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":596,"output":338,"cacheRead":102848,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":103782,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774609899424,"responseId":"19ce5a4d-58f3-4df0-8c8e-4a63fbb585b2"}}
