{"type":"message","id":"95199713","parentId":"8a2ee0ea","timestamp":"2026-03-27T11:34:15.382Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"我看到 openclaw.json 文件中有一个 `agents.list` 数组，里面包含了 `command`、`defense`、`offense` 三个代理的配置。新创建的6个代理（`offense-wireless`、`offense-recon` 等）没有被添加到这个列表中。所以网关无法识别它们。\n\n我需要编辑这个文件，把6个新代理的配置添加到 `agents.list` 数组中。但要注意保持原有结构。我可以基于现有的 `offense` 配置作为模板，创建6个新的条目，分别指向对应的代理目录。\n\n另外，还需要检查 `command` 代理的 `subagents.allowAgents` 字段，是否也需要添加这6个新代理的ID。\n\n现在开始编辑文件。首先备份原文件，然后进行修改。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_GaRitxR0LMKNGAemRjO396gp","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cp ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json.backup"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":19914,"output":395,"cacheRead":87040,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":107349,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774611240673,"responseId":"9f26cf9d-65ab-4b08-9bf0-d51d1429c47c"}}
