{"type":"message","id":"e58af5bf","parentId":"e4c8c8e5","timestamp":"2026-03-27T11:49:23.308Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"很好！看到最后一个结果是agent执行的（executionSource: \"agent\"），而之前的是api执行的。这说明新的消费者架构工作了。\n\n现在为每个专业化攻击者设置cron作业。我需要创建6个cron作业，每个运行agent_consumer.py并指定对应类别。\n\n但agent_consumer.py当前是模拟执行，实际应该调用代理的AI能力。也就是说，agent_consumer.py中的`execute_task_for_agent`函数应该调用DeepSeek API（使用代理的API密钥）。\n\n或者，更好的架构是：agent_consumer.py调用`openclaw agent --agent offense-<category> --message \"任务\"`。这样代理可以复用已有的配置和模型。\n\n让我修改agent_consumer.py，让它调用OpenClaw代理而不是直接模拟。但首先设置cron作业。\n\n先查看openclaw绑定帮助，解决通道问题。同时设置cron。让我尝试不同的绑定语法。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_AQsksMaZUUDS9nuxvbCRet4H","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"openclaw agents bind --help 2>&1 | head -30"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":6906,"output":437,"cacheRead":104256,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":111599,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774612151231,"responseId":"e13cfdc1-e456-45e1-88bc-189aae0a53f3"}}
{"type":"message","id":"f90ace20","parentId":"e58af5bf","timestamp":"2026-03-27T11:49:25.048Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_AQsksMaZUUDS9nuxvbCRet4H","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.23-2 (7ffe7e4) — iMessage green bubble energy, but for everyone.\n\nUsage: openclaw agents bind [options]\n\nAdd routing bindings for an agent\n\nOptions:\n  --agent <id>                  Agent id (defaults to current default agent)\n  --bind <channel[:accountId]>  Binding to add (repeatable). If omitted,\n                                accountId is resolved by channel defaults/hooks.\n                                (default: [])\n  -h, --help                    Display help for command\n  --json                        Output JSON summary (default: false)"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":1717,"aggregated":"🦞 OpenClaw 2026.3.23-2 (7ffe7e4) — iMessage green bubble energy, but for everyone.\n\nUsage: openclaw agents bind [options]\n\nAdd routing bindings for an agent\n\nOptions:\n  --agent <id>                  Agent id (defaults to current default agent)\n  --bind <channel[:accountId]>  Binding to add (repeatable). If omitted,\n                                accountId is resolved by channel defaults/hooks.\n                                (default: [])\n  -h, --help                    Display help for command\n  --json                        Output JSON summary (default: false)","cwd":"/home/asus/.openclaw/workspaces/command"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1774612165042}}
{"type":"message","id":"74d553b5","parentId":"f90ace20","timestamp":"2026-03-27T11:50:06.218Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"绑定语法是`--bind <channel[:accountId]>`。我需要知道可用的channel。可能是\"webchat\"，但之前说未知。让我检查当前的绑定状态。同时，我需要为每个专业化攻击者创建cron作业。\n\n但更重要的是，我需要修改agent_consumer.py，让它真正调用专业化攻击者代理，而不是模拟。这样每个代理才能真正\"消费\"事件。\n\n让我修改agent_consumer.py，调用openclaw命令执行任务。同时创建cron作业。\n\n先修改agent_consumer.py。然后为所有6个代理创建cron作业。同时检查通道绑定状态。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_YsDkiI3oGCdFatu5lYBTNM3u","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"/home/asus/.openclaw/events/agent_consumer.py","oldText":"def execute_task_for_agent(category, event):\n    \"\"\"执行任务（根据代理类别）\"\"\"\n    # 这里是代理特定的执行逻辑\n    # 实际实现中，代理会调用自己的模型/工具\n    # 这里简化为模拟执行\n    \n    task = event[\"task\"]\n    params = event.get(\"params\", {})\n    \n    print(f\"代理 {category} 执行任务: {task}\")\n    print(f\"参数: {json.dumps(params, indent=2)}\")\n    \n    # 模拟执行延迟\n    time.sleep(1)\n    \n    # 构建结果\n    result = {\n        \"success\": True,\n        \"data\": {\n            \"task\": task,\n            \"category\": category,\n            \"executedAt\": datetime.now(timezone.utc).isoformat(),\n            \"result\": f\"代理 {category} 成功执行任务 {task}\"\n        },\n        \"message\": f\"代理 {category} 完成任务\",\n        \"executionSource\": \"agent\"\n    }\n    \n    return result","newText":"def execute_task_for_agent(category, event):\n    \"\"\"执行任务（调用专业化攻击者代理）\"\"\"\n    task = event[\"task\"]\n    params = event.get(\"params\", {})\n    \n    print(f\"调用 {category} 代理执行任务: {task}\")\n    print(f\"参数: {json.dumps(params, indent=2)}\")\n    \n    # 构建任务消息\n    task_message = f\"执行任务: {task}\\n\"\n    task_message += f\"参数: {json.dumps(params, indent=2)}\\n\"\n    task_message += \"请返回 JSON 格式的结果，包含 'success' (布尔值)、'data' (执行结果) 和 'message' (可选描述) 字段。\"\n    \n    # 调用 OpenClaw 代理\n    import subprocess\n    try:\n        agent_id = f\"offense-{category}\"\n        cmd = [\"openclaw\", \"agent\", \"--agent\", agent_id, \"--message\", task_message, \"--json\"]\n        \n        print(f\"执行命令: {' '.join(cmd[:4])} ...\")\n        \n        # 运行命令，设置超时\n        result = subprocess.run(\n            cmd,\n            capture_output=True,\n            text=True,\n            timeout=60,  # 60秒超时\n            env={\"PATH\": \"/usr/local/bin:/usr/bin:/bin\"}  # 确保有基本路径\n        )\n        \n        if result.returncode != 0:\n            print(f\"代理调用失败 (退出码 {result.returncode}): {result.stderr[:200]}\")\n            return {\n                \"success\": False,\n                \"data\": {\n                    \"error\": f\"代理调用失败: {result.stderr[:100]}\",\n                    \"returncode\": result.returncode\n                },\n                \"message\": f\"代理 {category} 执行失败\",\n                \"executionSource\": \"agent\"\n            }\n        \n        # 解析代理响应\n        try:\n            agent_response = json.loads(result.stdout)\n            # 假设响应格式与API响应类似\n            if isinstance(agent_response, dict):\n                # 确保有正确的字段\n                if \"success\" not in agent_response:\n                    agent_response[\"success\"] = True\n                if \"data\" not in agent_response:\n                    agent_response[\"data\"] = agent_response\n                agent_response[\"executionSource\"] = \"agent\"\n                return agent_response\n            else:\n                return {\n                    \"success\": True,\n                    \"data\": {\"raw_response\": agent_response},\n                    \"message\": f\"代理 {category} 返回非JSON响应\",\n                    \"executionSource\": \"agent\"\n                }\n        except json.JSONDecodeError as e:\n            print(f\"代理响应不是有效的 JSON: {e}\")\n            # 尝试提取文本响应\n            return {\n                \"success\": True,\n                \"data\": {\"output\": result.stdout[:500]},\n                \"message\": f\"代理 {category} 返回文本响应\",\n                \"executionSource\": \"agent\"\n            }\n            \n    except subprocess.TimeoutExpired:\n        print(f\"代理调用超时 (60秒)\")\n        return {\n            \"success\": False,\n            \"data\": {\"error\": \"代理执行超时\"},\n            \"message\": f\"代理 {category} 执行超时\",\n            \"executionSource\": \"agent\"\n        }\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"代理调用异常: {e}\")\n        return {\n            \"success\": False,\n            \"data\": {\"error\": str(e)},\n            \"message\": f\"代理 {category} 调用异常\",\n            \"executionSource\": \"agent\"\n        }"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":2817,"output":1324,"cacheRead":107520,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":111661,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774612165051,"responseId":"f05d9df2-ecbf-49c3-b12e-94afa311bbbc"}}
