{"type":"message","id":"cde22cd8","parentId":"053e8449","timestamp":"2026-03-27T11:52:40.058Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"现在创建cron设置脚本，为所有6个专业化攻击者设置定期运行agent_consumer.py。同时，我需要调试openclaw agent调用问题。\n\n但时间有限，用户要求\"都执行\"。我需要同时推进：\n1. 创建cron作业\n2. 调试agent调用\n3. 路由绑定（可选）\n4. 测试其他代理\n\n让我先创建cron设置脚本。然后尝试手动测试openclaw agent命令，看看问题出在哪里。\n\n创建cron脚本。然后测试openclaw agent命令。同时思考是否需要路由绑定。实际上，如果代理通过cron定期检查队列，路由绑定可能不是必需的。但为了完整性，我可以尝试配置绑定。\n\n先创建cron脚本。然后测试openclaw agent。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_6MAawX09YDJ8qfRpSySrjBwR","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/asus/.openclaw/events/setup_agent_crons.py","content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\n为6个专业化攻击者代理设置cron作业\n每个代理每分钟检查一次事件队列\n\"\"\"\n\nimport subprocess\nimport sys\nfrom pathlib import Path\n\nEVENTS_DIR = Path(__file__).parent\nAGENT_CONSUMER = EVENTS_DIR / \"agent_consumer.py\"\n\n# 6个代理类别\nCATEGORIES = [\n    \"wireless\", \"recon\", \"web\", \"internal\", \"exploit\", \"social\"\n]\n\ndef get_current_crontab():\n    \"\"\"获取当前crontab内容\"\"\"\n    try:\n        result = subprocess.run(\n            [\"crontab\", \"-l\"],\n            capture_output=True,\n            text=True\n        )\n        if result.returncode == 0:\n            return result.stdout\n        else:\n            # 如果没有crontab，返回空字符串\n            return \"\"\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"获取crontab失败: {e}\")\n        return \"\"\n\ndef set_crontab(content):\n    \"\"\"设置crontab内容\"\"\"\n    try:\n        proc = subprocess.Popen(\n            [\"crontab\", \"-\"],\n            stdin=subprocess.PIPE,\n            text=True\n        )\n        proc.communicate(input=content)\n        if proc.returncode == 0:\n            return True\n        else:\n            print(f\"设置crontab失败 (返回码: {proc.returncode})\")\n            return False\n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"设置crontab异常: {e}\")\n        return False\n\ndef main():\n    print(\"为专业化攻击者代理设置cron作业\")\n    print(\"=\" * 50)\n    \n    if not AGENT_CONSUMER.exists():\n        print(f\"错误: 消费者脚本不存在: {AGENT_CONSUMER}\")\n        sys.exit(1)\n    \n    # 获取当前crontab\n    current_crontab = get_current_crontab()\n    \n    # 移除现有的代理消费者cron作业（如果有）\n    lines = current_crontab.split('\\n')\n    new_lines = []\n    \n    for line in lines:\n        # 保留不是代理消费者cron的行\n        if \"agent_consumer.py\" not in line and \"events/consume.py\" not in line:\n            new_lines.append(line)\n    \n    # 为每个代理添加cron作业\n    print(\"添加cron作业:\")\n    for category in CATEGORIES:\n        cron_line = f\"* * * * * cd {EVENTS_DIR} && /usr/bin/python3 {AGENT_CONSUMER} --category {category} >> {EVENTS_DIR}/{category}.log 2>&1\\n\"\n        new_lines.append(cron_line)\n        print(f\"  {category}: 每分钟检查一次\")\n    \n    # 添加一个注释行\n    new_lines.append(\"# 专业化攻击者代理消费者 (6个类别)\")\n    \n    # 构建新的crontab内容\n    new_crontab = '\\n'.join(new_lines).strip() + '\\n'\n    \n    # 显示将要设置的内容\n    print(f\"\\n新的crontab将有 {len(new_lines)} 行\")\n    \n    # 询问确认\n    response = input(\"\\n是否继续设置cron作业? (y/N): \").strip().lower()\n    if response != 'y':\n        print(\"取消设置\")\n        sys.exit(0)\n    \n    # 设置新的crontab\n    if set_crontab(new_crontab):\n        print(\"\\ncron作业设置成功!\")\n        print(f\"日志文件将保存到: {EVENTS_DIR}/*.log\")\n        print(\"\\n代理启动后，将每分钟检查一次事件队列。\")\n        \n        # 显示测试命令\n        print(\"\\n测试命令:\")\n        for category in CATEGORIES:\n            print(f\"  {category}: python3 {AGENT_CONSUMER} --category {category} --once\")\n        \n        # 显示监控命令\n        print(\"\\n监控命令:\")\n        print(f\"  查看队列状态: python3 {EVENTS_DIR}/status.py\")\n        print(f\"  查看日志: tail -f {EVENTS_DIR}/wireless.log\")\n    else:\n        print(\"\\ncron作业设置失败\")\n        sys.exit(1)\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    main()"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-reasoner","usage":{"input":2308,"output":1303,"cacheR